{"tid":1642083,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"香港踩非電動滑板車上行人路犯唔犯法","createTime":"2019-10-09T14:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T01:07:40.000Z","uid":84408,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a71517ff433d4278c3c9361ec3af9d9a23aded","tid":1642083,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"唔想搭黨鐵 去搭巴士又要行段路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行得多又辛苦 知電動板車踩邊都死<br />\n但真係唔知非電動踩上行人路是咪都唔得 有無巴打知"},{"pid":"ea93e998762fe95dcfd81581926f5b68e704e12b","tid":1642083,"uid":89287,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦而家"},{"pid":"3c6a82fac99a1df7d433b75924e1be66e0242e15","tid":1642083,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:01:06.000Z","msg":"支持警察 殺人都冇事"},{"pid":"2fb8d6afecf585f487a79bdcf3dd981921943027","tid":1642083,"uid":38761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"根據香港法例第374章&lt;道路交通條例&gt;第48條: <br />\n<br />\n任何使用道路的行人疏忽地危害其本人或他人的安全, 即屬犯罪, 可處罰款$500. <br />\n在香港行人路、馬路或沒有標示禁止滑板的公眾地方玩滑板, 有可能危害其本人或他人的安全, 所以是違法."},{"pid":"f182e82f2050e722aa956aafd1ea897735dae56c","tid":1642083,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"而家隨便拉人<br />\n有乜所謂"},{"pid":"fd63a5135a3aef2526075bccdd88a7966619b3fb","tid":1642083,"uid":33463,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"著為所欲為 tee 拎中國旗<br />\n咩事都沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47013eea22f0f61027ab695b6c2b4ad828c48156","tid":1642083,"uid":64093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"行過都犯法啦，理得你踩住個根斗雲咩"},{"pid":"a0468c0a9bd1d1e0e8e7cc95896303b063087382","tid":1642083,"uid":214926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy